== Roadmap ==

|=Phase|=Status|=What It Unlocks
|**Alpha**|Current|Invite-based access, full pipeline, quality validation
|**Beta**|Planned|User authentication, performance optimization, monitoring
|**V1.0**|Planned|Public REST API, browser extensions, ClaimReview schema
|**V1.5+**|Vision|Live audio/video fact-checking, CMS plugins, team workspaces

