== Contribution Options ==

Non-financial support is equally valuable — especially at this stage:

|=Contribution|=What It Means|=Who Could Help
|**Beta testing & feedback**|Early access to new features; feedback on verdict quality and usability|Journalists, fact-checkers, researchers
|**Domain expertise**|Fact-checking methodology advice, legal review, LLM evaluation|Practicing fact-checkers, media lawyers, AI researchers
|**Code contributions**|Bug fixes, features, performance optimization on the open-source codebase|Developers, university students (thesis projects)
|**Translation & localization**|Documentation, UI, and prompt translation (DE/FR/IT/EN)|Multilingual contributors
|**Data contributions**|Multilingual test claims, curated evidence sources, evaluation datasets|Researchers, journalism schools
|**Advocacy & outreach**|Share FactHarbor with journalists, educators, and researchers|Anyone who sees the value
|**Advisory circle**|Lightweight guidance (2–4 hours/month) on strategy, methodology, or partnerships|Domain experts, media professionals

----

== How We Protect Your Trust ==

FactHarbor's governance ensures that funding never compromises editorial independence.

|=Safeguard|=Detail
|**20% rule**|No single donor may finance more than 20% of the annual budget (exception: competitive public grants)
|**Rejection criteria**|Political parties, media companies, pharma, and any donor demanding editorial control are refused
|**Full transparency**|All funders above CHF 5,000 published by name and amount. Annual financial report.
|**Mission lock**|Swiss Verein statutes prohibit profit distribution — surplus is irrevocably reinvested
|**Editorial firewall**|Donors have zero influence on claims analyzed, verdicts produced, or methodology used
|**IFCN alignment**|Governance aligns with the International Fact-Checking Network Code of Principles

----

== Swiss Non-Profit Structure ==

(% class="box infomessage" style="background-color:#eef3f8;border-color:#9db4cb;" %)
(((
The FactHarbor **[[Verein>>https://github.com/robertschaub/FactHarbor/blob/main/Docs/Legal/DRAFT_Vereinsstatuten_FactHarbor_DE.md]]** is currently in preparation. Tax-exempt status will be applied for upon registration.
)))

|=Aspect|=Detail
|**Legal form**|Swiss Verein (Association) under Art. 60 ff. ZGB
|**Purpose**|Promote informed opinion-forming through evidence-based tools — non-profit, public-benefit
|**Neutrality**|Politically and religiously neutral, no substantial political activities
|**Prohibited funding**|Advertising revenue, user data sales, outcome-conditional payments
|**Dissolution**|Assets transfer to an organisation with comparable public-benefit purpose

